      "headline": "Why Glendale Chooses Westgate Enterprises, LLC for Superior Electrical Work",
      "benefits": [
        {
          "title": "Enhanced Safety for Your Property",
          "description": "Our meticulous approach to every electrical task ensures that your home or business is not only powered efficiently but also operates with the highest safety standards, protecting your loved ones and assets.",
