        "alt": "Stock image illustrating 'Customer Satisfaction Guaranteed' section, showing a handshake."
      },
      {
        "title": "Lighting Installation & Repair",
        "description": "From ambient to task lighting, we design and install interior and exterior lighting solutions, including LED conversions.",
